{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/radioactive-waste-management/about/procurement","content_id":"fee71443-0b11-4593-8482-6cdc6ff2869c","description":"Tendering for contracts and transparency","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":false,"alternative_format_contact_email":"rwmfeedback@nda.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"60c76090d3bf7f4bd738672e","filename":"Procurement_Delivery_Plan_June_2021.pdf"},{"asset_manager_id":"60c76090d3bf7f4bd6a9bc72","filename":"thumbnail_Procurement_Delivery_Plan_June_2021.pdf.png"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":182477,"filename":"Procurement_Delivery_Plan_June_2021.pdf","id":"5299509","number_of_pages":4,"title":"Procurement Delivery Plan","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60c76090d3bf7f4bd738672e/Procurement_Delivery_Plan_June_2021.pdf"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>To comply with government regulations, we use an approach based on the value of the contract, and whether a public-sector contract already exists that can be used:</p>\n\n<p>We use 3 systems to advertise and to manage our contracts:</p>\n\n<ol>\n  <li>\n    <p>Framework Contracts awarded by Crown Commercial Services or other procurement hubs for utilisation by the wider public sector <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/crown-commercial-service\" class=\"govuk-link\">Government Procurement Service website</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>New procurement opportunities with a cumulative value of over £25,000 <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder\" class=\"govuk-link\">Contracts Finder website</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>New higher-value procurement opportunities with a cumulative total over the current EU threshold <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.find-tender.service.gov.uk/Search\" class=\"govuk-link\">Find a Tender</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>All public-sector procurements are subject to European Commission (EC) Treaty principles of non-discrimination, equal treatment and transparency.</p>\n\n<p>RWM will publish all contract awards over £25,000 on <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder\" class=\"govuk-link\">Contracts Finder website</a></p>\n\n<p>Commercial pipelines provide a forward look of potential commercial activity within a department. The information presented is for reference only and reflects the Radioactive Waste Management (RWM) anticipated procurement pipeline.</p>\n\n<p>RWM makes no commitment that:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the requirements identified in this table will be procured</li>\n  <li>the value of any contract will be as stated</li>\n  <li>the timing of any future procurement exercises will be as stated</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The sourcing route for any subsequent procurement has not been determined, for example it could be via frameworks managed by <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.crowncommercial.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\">Crown Commercial Services (CCS)</a> or open competitions.</p>\n\n<p>RWM cannot guarantee that these opportunities will be available to all suppliers.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/60c76090d3bf7f4bd738672e/Procurement_Delivery_Plan_June_2021.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.